### -----------------------

### Get All Warehouses
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Warehouse
# @name createWarehouse
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Main Warehouse",
